_sText:
This is the latest version of Zm_ryan_valley.bsp.
 
1-U can climb gutters on this map (not all, so u will have to try and see) , some of them are pointed with an arrow.

2-Fixed the skybox error.


3-Added more physics in order to make better barricades.


4-There is no fog now.


5-Some walls and vents can be destroyed.
